<TEXT>
   Gospel music singer Twila Paris has
written an anthem for a forthcoming project by the Lausanne
Committee for World Evangelism founded by the Rev. Billy Graham.
   The project is ``Target 2000: Great Commission Torch Run.''
Relay teams of young people in various countries are to carry
torches symbolizing the gospel of Jesus with the goal of
evangelizing all countries by the year 2000.
