   Robert Campeau, triumphant after winning the
takeover battle for Federated Department Stores Inc., says he wants
to expand the retailer but he'll improve productivity even if it
means layoffs.
   ``There will be some streamlining,'' Campeau said Tuesday. ``You
cannot survive and compete by having jobs and jobs and jobs.''
